<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT7">
<l>immaiyai maṟumai taṉṉai yemakkuvī ṭāki niṉṟa</l>
<l>meymmaiyai virinta cōlai viyaṉṟiru varaṅkam mēya</l>
<l>cemmaiyaik karumai taṉṉait tirumalai yorumai yāṉai</l>
<l>taṉmaiyai niṉaivā reṉṟaṉ ṟalaimicai maṉṉu vārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This life, the next, the truth which endures as liberation for us,</l>
<l>The Red [one] who dwells in vast Tiruvaraṅkam with expansive groves,</l>
<l>The Black [one], Tirumalai’s unique [Lord] -</l>
<l>Those who think on his nature [thus] are fixed on my own head.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
